Scott Pembroke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scott_Pembroke 0 Scott Pembroke (September 13, 1889 – February 21, 1951) was an American director, actor and screenwriter. He directed 73 films between 1920 and 1937. He was born in San Francisco, California and died in Pasadena, California.
